user.biography: Gina Homolka - Sunset chaser ☀️ Food, travel, wine & beach lover. NYTBS author 5 cookbooks. Tag #skinnytaste for a chance to be featured. 5M + on FB

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skinnytaste Healthy Recipes on August 16, 2021. May be an image of food and indoor.

node.text:
People always ask my what my last meal on earth would be, and I would probably say fried chicken! The real kind!! But most nights, to make it healthier I make it in the oven or air fryer which is just as good! This version I remove the skin, coat it with a Dijon-mayo and seasoned crushed seasoned bran flakes. It comes out so crispy and delish! Curios what your last meal on earth would be?? 👇🏼
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

node.text:
I have big news! December is going to be an exciting month!! You all know my new cookbook SKINNYTASTE AIR FRYER DINNERS is on sale 12/14. WELL, the new SKINNYTASTE ULTIMATE MEAL PLANNER is ALSO on sale in December, 12/7 to be exact! 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
A 52-week meal planner to help you plan your meals ahead and keep you organized. 👊🏼✍🏼 The pages tear out if you want to hang them on your fridge. Plus a 12 week meal plan including 30 recipes (15 new) and tear-out grocery lists. Swipe right for a sneak peek. Available at Indie Bound, Barnes and Noble and Amazon, and see link in profile to preorder now!  https://amzn.to/3jPrMy0 (affil link) #mealplanner #mealplanning #getorganized #writeitdownmakeithappen
